name: Tommy Swiss
tag_list: mattress, bed-frames, beds, furniture, designer-furniture, replica-furniture, office-chairs, lounge-chairs, outdoor-furniture
overview:
Tommy Swiss is a revolutionary furniture and homewares fashion label with a direct manufacturer to consumer online business model.

A vertically integrated business, Tommy Swiss manufactures premium quality products, bypassing all middlemen and intermediaries via its innovative online retail platform. This allows Tommy Swiss to delivers all its products without the high street mark ups, saving consumers up to 80%.

Currently based in Melbourne, Australia - Tommy Swiss is the number 1 place to go for Australians when on the hunt for beds, mattresses, sofas, tables, chairs and other designer furniture and home furnishing products.
